---
title: Mexican Beef & Black Bean Burrito Bowl with Spinach Rice, Sour Cream & Tomato Salsa
description: Embark on a culinary fiesta with our Mexican burrito bowl, where black beans and beef are simmered in a tomato-based sauce and served alongside a zesty tomato salsa and cooling sour cream. This vibrant bowl is a symphony of flavours, delivering a taste of Mexico in every satisfying bite!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65a067261ee0609964a9c9cf-99527811.jpeg
